    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Exporter freshness",
      "description": "Seconds since the gateway last exported OTLP metrics. Spikes when the gateway process is idle or restarting; hook activity may continue via audit logs.\n\ncovered_by:\n  - defenseclaw_telemetry_exporter_last_export_ts_seconds → internal/telemetry/provider.go",
